# How to build
- You will use following commands

```shell
#!/bin/bash
xcodebuild \
    -scheme BonsaiExample \
    -destination "platform=visionOS Simulator,name=Apple Vision Pro" \
    -configuration Debug \
    build
```

# How to check lint

You will check and fix the linter error when you make the code changes.

```shell
swiftlint lint .
```